{"tid":1885841,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方拘捕3人涉搶廁紙案　疑犯相信廁紙有價可轉售圖利！","createTime":"2020-02-18T14:28:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T15:02:11.000Z","uid":63113,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"24ded9e8219f3539df778dd2659c1c6ee6d2ff3a","tid":1885841,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:28:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd66703e92f7da79d3d68fe63b4167e5c4ec19f4","tid":1885841,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:28:59.000Z","msg":"旺角昨晨有人持刀搶走千多元廁紙的案件，警方再拘捕多一名男子，共拘捕3人。<br />\n<br />\n旺角警區總督察周嘉文表示，案發生昨日清晨6時，一名送貨工人把貨物放在旺角道及洗衣街交界一間超級市場外，一名疑犯用硬物指向工人，並用手推車劫走50條廁紙，向深水埗方向逃去。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報搜查，在案發現場附近一間賓館尋回該批廁紙，並在賓館內拘捕兩名懷疑涉案、報稱賓館職員的50及55歲男子。到今日傍晚時，警方在旺角區再拘捕一名報稱無業的26歲男子，懷疑與案件有關。3名男子均被通宵扣查，不排除有更多人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n周嘉文表示，3名疑犯相識，為本地人，相信他們認為廁紙有轉售價值，可以轉售圖利，而其中一人有黑社會背景。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509333-20200218.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509333-20200218.htm&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmlLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=736cb890\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509333-20200218.htm&h=3e5094c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509333-20200218.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5b1e9df634cb613427e6dfb9660f43a6241ca63c","tid":1885841,"uid":63113,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:30:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">相信他們認為廁紙有轉售價值，可以轉售圖利</span>，而其中一人有黑社會背景。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sz8udjF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSz8udjF.gif&h=844e1b65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45acf93216a64820c27cd99cb457c9a62e9a6dde","tid":1885841,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:32: